data.title: About — Emily Penrose
data.text:
—

Meet Emily, a passionate photographer whose journey began with a deep love for capturing moments in time. With a Bachelor of Arts in Photography, Emily brings both formal training and a decade of professional experience to their craft. Their photography style aims to combine the candid documentary style of photography with lifestyle and brand photography by using movement and lighting to evoke a natural feel in their images.

What truly sets Emily apart in the industry is her ability to connect with clients on a personal level, stemming from a genuine love for meeting new people. Specializing in portraits and food and beverage photography, she finds particular joy in capturing the essence of the culinary world, a passion that originated from her own beginnings in the industry. Whether it's a bustling restaurant or a serene outdoor setting, Emily finds inspiration in every location. The excitement she feels for collaborating with clients to exceed their expectations and ensure each moment captured is imbued with authenticity and satisfaction is present at every shoot.
